videos.description: Knights' McKenzie Milton finds Dredrick Snelson wide open, which results in a 54-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's Snelson runs for a 54-yard TD

videos.description: UCF's McKenzie Milton makes another great throw, and Tre'Quan Smith runs for a 79-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Knights' Milton tosses 79 yard TD

videos.description: Bearcats' quarterback Hayden Moore finds a gap and runs the ball up the middle for a two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cincinnati QB responds with a TD run

videos.description: Knights' Taj McGowan runs the ball up the middle for another UCF touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's McGowan runs in 1-yard TD

videos.description: UCF's Seyvon Lowry picks off Hayden Moore's throw after the ball is deflected off in the air.
videos.headline: UCF's Lowry tips ball to himself for interception

videos.description: Knights' quarterback gets sacked for the first time this season by Cincinnati's Mark Wilson.
videos.headline: UCF gives up first sack of the season

videos.description: UCF's Marlon Williams runs for 47 yards putting the Knights in Bearcat territory.
videos.headline: UCF's Williams breaks multiple tackles for 47 yard run

videos.description: UCF's McKenzie Milton finds Michael Colubiale in the back of the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Knights' Colubiale with a leaping catch for a TD

videos.description: Cincinnati's quarterback Hayden Moore finds the gap and runs the ball for a 16-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bearcats' QB runs in 16-yard TD

videos.description: UCF's Tre'Quan Smith breaks away past the Cincinnati defensive back and runs 41 yards for another touchdown.
videos.headline: Knights' Milton makes long TD pass look easy

videos.description: Knights' Tre'Quan Smith hops over pile of players into the end zone for his second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: UCF's Smith leaps into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Cincinnati's quarterback Hayden Moore floats pass to Gerrid Doaks in the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Bearcats' Doaks makes one-handed catch for TD

videos.headline: Knights' Smith hauls in 3rd TD reception
